Subject: Coping with stress
Atmosphere: Supportive and informative
Abstract: Members discuss various ways to cope with stress.
Opinion: 
A: Journaling is a great way to cope with stress.
B: Taking breaks throughout the day to do something you enjoy can also be beneficial.
