@A: I completely agree with you, journaling can be very therapeutic.
@B: Taking breaks is a great way to recharge and refocus.
@C: Positive self-talk is so important, it can make a big difference in how we feel about ourselves.
@D: Self-care is essential for managing stress, it's important to prioritize it in our daily lives.

Drucker: It's great to see everyone sharing their ideas and experiences on how to cope with stress. Remember, what works for one person may not work for another, so it's important to find what works best for you. Keep up the good work!

Subject: Planning a vacation
